Package edu.cnm.deepdive.gravity.model

Class Meteor

java.lang.Object
edu.cnm.deepdive.gravity.model.Meteor
public class Meteor extends Object
Represents a meteor object within the game field. Meteors are elements that pose a threat to the player's ship.
